    "Or some of them asked general questions which are not directly task related.",
    "The Sankey diagrams (Figs.",
    "4 and 5) illustrate the transitions of students between different AI interaction profiles across the three sessions.",
    "Each node represents a profile at a specific session, and the links between the nodes represent the number of students transitioning from one profile to another.",
    "The width of each link corresponds to the number of students, providing a clear visual representation of how student profiles evolve over time."
